        <abstract> 
<p>Has given in <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> 2: 12, an account from AG of the brushes on the sides of <hi rend="italic">Monacanthus</hi>; has now learned of brush-like scales on the males of <hi rend="italic">Mallotus</hi>. Asks whether the two genera are related.</p> 
